channel.title: Cry Macho
channel.desc: Thriller 2021 An ex-rodeo star is requested to escort the son of his former boss to Mexico away from his troubled mother. On the road, both the man and the boy have to face their understanding of masculinity and redefine what it really means to be macho. Clint Eastwood, Dwight Yoakam, Daniel V. Graulau, Amber Lynn Ashley, Eduardo Minett, Ivan Hernandez, Fernanda Urrejola, Clint Eastwood, Nick Schenk, N. Richard Nash.
